Gemini

Level up your app development

infotip:
Gemini in Firebase is included with Gemini Code Assist, which is available to try at no cost until November 8th, 2024, limited to one user per billing account. Licenses can be purchased in Cloud Billing.
infonote:
Required APIs We will enable the Gemini for Google Cloud API in the project mad-project to use Gemini in Firebase. Learn More
Use of the API is subject to the Google Cloud Platform Terms of Service and Service Specific Terms applicable to Generative AI services.
Disclaimers:
  • Gemini in Firebase is a work in progress. It may display inaccurate information that doesn't represent Google's views.
  • Avoid using generated code in production unless you test it first.
  • If you enable Gemini in Firebase, it will have access to your Firebase environment. Responses may be tailored to your app.
  • Your prompts aren't used to train the model. Learn more about how we train our models
